<p>We can now define the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Logit" ti=
tle=3D"Logit">logit</a> (log odds) function as the inverse <span class=3D"m=
we-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inl=
ine mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://ww=
w.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyle g=3D\sigma ^{-1}}">
