d two categories (male and female).</figcaption></figure>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Many_explanatory_variables,=
_two_categories"><span id=3D"Many_explanatory_variables.2C_two_categories">=
</span>Many explanatory variables, two categories</h3><span class=3D"mw-edi=
