<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"As_a_latent-variable_model"=
>As a latent-variable model</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=
=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/i=
