=3Db_{0}+b_{1}x}"></span>. The fit is obtained by choosing the <i>b</i> par=
ameters which minimize the sum of the squares of the residuals (the squared=
 error term) for each data point:
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
