ral of the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chi-squared_distributio=
n" title=3D"Chi-squared distribution">chi-squared distribution</a> with one=
 degree of freedom from 11.6661... to infinity is equal to 0.00063649...
</p><p>This effectively means that about 6 out of a 10,000 fits to random <=
i>y<sub>k</sub></i> can be expected to have a better fit (smaller deviance)=
